    <item>
      <title>英国在债券市场中被“欺负”，因为收益率飙升至27年高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/uk-borrowing-costs-hit-highest-since-1998-amid-global-bond-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国的长期借贷成本在唐宁街上的27年高，堆积的压力大于英国财政状况不稳定，因为人们担心金融体系中的压力达到了一个突破点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/uk-borrowing-costs-hit-highest-since-1998-amid-global-bond-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 07:38:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的互惠关税开始时，美国股票鞭打</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/us-stock-futures-swing-as-tariffs-kick-in-china-levies-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济衰退的担忧和一系列与贸易有关的头条新闻，美国股票在收益和损失之间闪烁，而在公司估值大幅下降之后，一些与贸易相关的头条新闻陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/us-stock-futures-swing-as-tariffs-kick-in-china-levies-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 07:37:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加深贸易战减弱了需求前景，欧洲天然气下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/europe-gas-drops-with-broader-financial-markets-as-tariffs-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格下跌至七个月的低点，因为世界上两个最大的经济体之间的贸易争端不断升级，这加剧了对能源的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/europe-gas-drops-with-broader-financial-markets-as-tariffs-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 06:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场撤退，作为美国国债，全球范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2020年大流行以来，美国国债的回调迅速飙升，随着投资者出售政府债券以筹集现金，这本来可以成为金融动荡和流浪市场的避风港的损失加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 05:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国对我们征收关税，石油的崩溃加深了60美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加剧贸易战的濒临灭绝的能源需求，石油跌至四年低点，美国和中国的新浪潮使全球经济息息相关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>代理主席说，FDIC可以简化银行的生物意愿。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/fdic-to-ease-banks-living-will-mandates-acting-chair-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦存款保险公司代理主席特拉维斯·希尔（Travis Hill）表示，该机构将放弃银行所谓的生活遗嘱的要求，因此它们不再围绕假设的失败情况建立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/fdic-to-ease-banks-living-will-mandates-acting-chair-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
